{"text_id":185715,"tokens":["This"," work"," tackles"," the"," long","-","standing"," problem"," of"," dedu","cing"," free"," ferm","ion"," resolutions"," of"," super","group"," W","Z","NW"," models","."," Motiv","ated"," by"," the"," connection"," between"," these"," models"," and"," various"," condensed"," matter"," systems",","," we"," employ"," a"," systematic"," algebraic"," approach"," to"," explicitly"," resolve"," the"," super","algebra"," associated"," with"," the"," W","Z","NW"," models"," into"," a"," free"," ferm","ion"," algebra","."," ","\n\n","Our"," key"," idea"," revolves"," around"," introducing"," appropriate"," twisted"," boundary"," conditions"," on"," the"," underlying"," quantum"," group"," associated"," with"," the"," super","group","."," This"," procedure"," allows"," us"," to"," obtain"," a"," set"," of"," local"," ferm","ion"," fields"," that"," faithfully"," reproduce"," all"," the"," algebraic"," structures"," of"," the"," original"," W","Z","NW"," model","."," ","\n\n","Through"," this"," construction",","," we"," unravel"," the"," connection"," between"," the"," super","group"," W","Z","NW"," models"," and"," their"," free"," ferm","ion"," representation","."," This"," resolution"," not"," only"," provides"," a"," microscopic"," understanding"," of"," these"," models"," but"," also"," opens"," doors"," for"," exploring"," their"," potential"," applications"," in"," various"," condensed"," matter"," and"," high","-","energy"," physics"," contexts","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}